query:
SELECT e.id, e.gamePresenterId, e.evaluationDate, gp.name, gp.teamId
FROM evaluations e
JOIN game_presenters gp ON e.gamePresenterId = gp.id
WHERE gp.teamId = 1
LIMIT 10;
